<HEADLINE>
FT  01 SEP 94 / World News in Brief: Britain pressed to pull out of World
Cup
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The International Amateur Athletic Federation urged Britain to withdraw its
women's team from next week's World Cup after the second sample of a drugs
test taken from 800-metres runner Diane Modahl proved positive. Modahl
pledged to prove her innocence.
