FT  31 AUG 94 / Northumberland Tec: Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Northumberland Training and Enterprise Council was inadvertently excluded
from a league table last Friday listing the top ten Tecs, based on the
number of people achieving a job after completing the Training for Work
programme.
Northumberland Tec achieved 32.1 'positive outcomes' per 100 leavers,
putting it eighth in the table.
