<HEADLINE>
FT  30 AUG 94 / UK Company News: Fleming Claverhouse net assets edge ahead
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Fleming Claverhouse Investment Trust had a net asset value of 195.9p per
share at June 30, a modest improvement on 193p a year earlier.
Attributable revenue for the six months to end-June amounted to Pounds 1.5m,
up from Pounds 1.12m, for earnings of 2.71p (2.55p). A second interim
dividend of 1.25p maintains the total to date at 2.5p.
</TEXT>
